com.yworks.yfiles.layout.router.polyline

Interface IDecompositionListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IGraphPartitionExtension
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphPartition, GraphPartitionExtensionAdapter

    public interface IDecompositionListener
    This interface is implemented by classes that require to be notified of changes in IPartitions.

    Implementations are notified when PartitionCells are created, divided, and/or finalized.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onCellCreated(PartitionCell createdCell)
      Callback after the new given PartitionCell has been created.
      void onCellFinalized(PartitionCell finalizedCell)
      Callback after the given PartitionCell has been finalized and won't be further subdivided.
      void onCellSubdivided(PartitionCell cell, List<Object> subCells)
      Callback after the given PartitionCell has been subdivided into several sub-cells.

      • onCellSubdivided

        void onCellSubdivided(PartitionCell cell,
                      List<Object> subCells)
        Callback after the given PartitionCell has been subdivided into several sub-cells.

        IDecompositionListener may not modify the list of sub-cells.

        Parameters:
        cell - the cell that has been subdivided
        subCells - the sub-cells resulting from the subdivision of the given PartitionCell
